	<p:descriptions>
		<p:description descriptionType="Abstract">The Unidata Integrated
			Data
			Viewer (IDV) is a software application for analyzing and
			displaying geoscience data. The IDV emphasizes interactive
			three-dimensional visualization and integration of diverse data
			types. The IDV software is available for Windows, Mac OS X, and
			various flavors
			of Unix including Linux, and Solaris.
		</p:description>
